{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/header_logo.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><strong>Mirror Layers is a first person social horror game. <br>Explore the mysterious apartment 12, cooperate with other players to solve challenging puzzles and survive the horrors of the Mirror, a distorted reality tainted by tragedy.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/section_1.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/socialfinal4.gif?t=1720814095\" /><br>To proceed in Mirror Layers it's necessary to interact with other players through a social network called <i>Propaganda</i>. Here you will be able to share advice, opinions and especially items with other people. The game also provides tools with which you can take notes and pictures; remember, &quot;sharing&quot; is caring!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/app.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><strong>Propaganda web/android app is now available!</strong> Cooperate with other players while you're away from MirrorOS!<br>Webapp: <br>GooglePlay: <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/section_2.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/enigmi.gif?t=1720814095\" /><br>The focus of the game is to solve increasingly varied and complex puzzles, exploring the environment, collecting clues, important objects and collaborating through Propaganda.<br>But beware, once you're through the Mirror's threshold you will not be safe anymore...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/section_3.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/buck.gif?t=1720814095\" /><br>The reality behind the Mirror has more than one way to put you in danger. A creature lies within the Mirror, one moved only by its instinct to search for <i>something</i>... A <i>part of you</i>, maybe? <br>There's more: negative emotions permeates this place, phantoms of a dark past that will torment you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/section_4.png?t=1720814095\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/mlgif3.gif?t=1720814095\" /><br>In Mirror Layers the player acts as themselves. <br>You received an anonymous invitation to Apartment 12 of Chandran Building, a bizarre 16 stories tall apartment complex whose walls hold a dark secret.<br><i>Will you join the game?</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>WE ASK YOU TO GIVE US A PART OF YOU. PART OF YOUR IDENTITY.</i></strong></h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/clock_big.gif?t=1720814095\" /><br><br><strong>I made contact. <i>What are you waiting for?</i></strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Take a look in the Mirror","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1490980/ea55bb2b9bfb03c9504f34f6fd9df6532533ec1a.jpg"},{"name":"To the stars and beyond","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1490980/397eb16aa8b53fc5245196be9dce6f0f3c620279.jpg"},{"name":"Florice is now open","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1490980/5011f40159d7bae5ff0cf858b6902f1bba81ae75.jpg"},{"name":"????????????","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1490980/014624f126f5